## ✅ ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA COMPLETED

All acceptance criteria have been satisfied:

1. **✅ Sidebar hidden on screens < 768px** - Added `hidden md:block` classes to Sidebar.tsx
2. **✅ Hamburger menu button appears in header on mobile** - Created MobileNav.tsx with hamburger button that shows on mobile (`md:hidden`)
3. **✅ Clicking hamburger opens sidebar as overlay** - Implemented slide-in sidebar with dark overlay background
4. **✅ Clicking outside overlay closes it** - Added click-outside handler in MobileNav.tsx
5. **✅ Clicking nav link closes overlay and navigates** - Each navigation link has `onClick={() => setIsOpen(false)}` to close the overlay when clicked

The mobile navigation is now fully functional with:
- Responsive breakpoint at 768px (md: breakpoint)
- Smooth transitions and animations
- Proper z-index layering for overlay
- Automatic closing on route changes
- Accessibility features (aria-label on hamburger button)
